de.uniks.se1ss19teamb.rbsg.sockets

Class GameSocketDistributor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uniks.se1ss19teamb.rbsg.sockets.GameSocketDistributor

  • public class GameSocketDistributor
extends java.lang.Object
    Distributes the GameSocket instances so any class can take the GameSocket that it needs. Whether it's the GameSocket for the main player or for one of the up to 3 extra players that are bots. The main GameSocket should be on place 0.
